      "matters": "For Subsequent Administration And Confirmation Of Final Order<br>Off Calendar Jun-23-2014 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: John Bryant for George Hugenberg (Petitioner).<br><br>With respect to the Missouri property, Mr. Bryant stated that he was told by two Attorney's that the Missouri Court needs a will that was probated within one year of the Decedent's death or a current order for final distribution that was issued within one year. Counsel suggested using Probate Code 9611. The Petition for Subsequent Administration and Confirmation of Final Order was taken under submission. Counsel is to submit a proposed order.  <br><br>Judge: Mary E. Wiss. Clerk: Rosie Noguera. Bailiff: Deputy A. Allen. (Not Reported)",
